{"tid":347190,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日比人話天然呆同個樣太林","createTime":"2017-08-04T15:04:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T15:17:35.000Z","uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7cbae636f93a1da3c38f4dcf88c3e4e00570d9d","tid":347190,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:04:26.000Z","msg":"明明我經常想西口西臉唔好咁易比人恰同扮成熟，<br />\n但都成日比人話我點惡都係天然呆可愛樣<br />\n細路仔係唔識惡樣架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最怕一陣比人以為我對人有意思，比左個假希望人就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9824869e28426475b1e6117db773e54fac7acf","tid":347190,"uid":71826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:10:16.000Z","msg":"細路仔扮大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbed548527c59842fb4c591adfb83a4cfd189835","tid":347190,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:12:08.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"e1c1ebee0d8569009022a9ce57e1f330f2f87ab7","tid":347190,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細路仔扮大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人總要長大"},{"pid":"d414ea2cc4178229d579c8fefcc073bce2768618","tid":347190,"uid":62062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:15:11.000Z","msg":"好過唔笑就比人話西"},{"pid":"39776fb70487c77d1bf58c02a8439bfce419213e","tid":347190,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好過唔笑就比人話西</blockquote><br />\n明明我西面都比人當笑面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}